OL,5, Proposed changes to how disabled people
OL,6, receive care in Bristol have left      
OL,7, residents fearing they could be        
OL,8, re-located to care homes to save money.
OL,10,FBristol City Council has released draft
OL,11,Fplans as a result of "facing a cost of 
OL,12,Foperating crisis".                     
OL,14,FIt says shared accommodation including 
OL,15,Fresidential homes might be considered  
OL,16,Fif care in the home is too expensive.  
OL,18,FMark Williams, who has 24-hour care,   
OL,19,Fsays: "My worry is my care will be cut 
OL,20,Fand I will end up in a care home."     
